Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明年的秋天 還能看得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太陽早去睡覺 星星月亮就會通宵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:02:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在晚上之前結束所有祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}耶魯節之夜就要來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好 夜之愛子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能做好耶魯節的準備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}耶魯節？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在就去做耶魯節的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這個瞌睡蟲 耶魯節很快就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要燃燒耶魯的柴薪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在黑色女神和冥府之鹿走上原野之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你們 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}耶魯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們總會在冬至到來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我叫她們耶魯的雙子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過不知道她們到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天會很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}累了要跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一定會說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不配當使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:16.62,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世有危險時 我什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他一直都這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:20.28,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣沒意義吧 我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你比我更了解智世吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世會對我隱瞞 你可能也不好告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是你可以早點跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如此一來 我就想辦法處理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是尷尬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她的身體還有點冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為剛從外面回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}開始準備耶魯節吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是漂亮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是這麼覺得的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在檞寄生枝下接吻是種傳統習俗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他好像很想試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你可以彎下腰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}換我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在背後 還是腰部 有一種癢癢的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲也來一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來吃晚餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老爺 您的東西我收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思 每次都拖到最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會 這點事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題 已經留了紙條
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人好多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 我先進到裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思啊 把你叫到倫敦來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 是…關於聖誕禮物的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}送給連富烈德的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真的不知道送什麼好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前送什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反而是他送我禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我想今年送他點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直在吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吃得好猛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你…你不送些什麼給那個骷髏頭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全沒想過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 今天我們就一起去挑禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一臉要我陪著的意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有找到好東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有 畢竟要考慮到他的喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實我根本不知道他的喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我從沒送禮物給什麼人過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是…沒什麼認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身邊沒有這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那現在 我和智世就是同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然魔法和魔術不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但都是跟著師父學習生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:09:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是恩滋華斯老爺家的小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黑澤爾先生 您好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 你在和誰說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呀 和您一起的那位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}魔術師和魔法使不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們看不到施展了隱身魔法的我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}初次見面 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聖誕禮物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}選個能想像出對方使用的樣子的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:11:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仔細回想一下對方 想想最適合的東西是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們再去逛一圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}平常使用的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我好像想到了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好狡猾 快告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能學我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是愛麗絲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們走 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了 跟以前一樣和我玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經不碰毒品了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從…從哪裡冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:11:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 他們是我以前的狐群狗黨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}毒品很好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好吃 不合我的口味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也不是喜歡才去吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在都覺得是做了場夢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種事沒什麼意思 不說了不說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我被混蛋父母逼著吸食毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原本只有當毒販這一條路可走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是師父收留了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 你有沒有看到一個金髮的小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我得好好教訓她一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看什麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想一直待在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還沒和你自我介紹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫米海爾‧連富烈德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}隨便你怎麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先洗個澡再說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那時候我還完全不相信師父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前一直生活在垃圾場般的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信任他人 對我來說是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}書名看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是說了不要翻開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我也有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我沒有下明確的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你受傷了 臉上…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是幸好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好不容易恢復了健康
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可不能再受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我習慣幫人治傷了 能做好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然都是自學的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次我會好好做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要作為守護者 保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回想起來真是不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不知道該說什麼才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不需要你去考慮什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的幸福還是不幸 是你自己決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你聽我說了這些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說有沒有一隻使魔鳥 飛到你那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很小隻的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算了 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會再寫信的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你陪我到這麼晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會 也謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望我們都順利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你交到朋友真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大哥哥覺得她合格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}倒不是個壞傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 伊森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉 伊森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們也回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎回來 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回來得真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回來了 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼想要的東西值得跑去倫敦一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還和連富烈德的弟子見了面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知道你都碰過多少危險了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然還什麼都不說就出門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我怕你不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我肯定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:18:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有我跟著的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用這麼生氣 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}生氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我是為了去買這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然早了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊 沒想到你會送我禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前沒想過要給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃…你一直都戴著同樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想說這能讓你安心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是你不喜歡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也給你一份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然只幫安潔莉卡她們做過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但這次我想給你也做一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是你親手做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}安潔莉卡以前和我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想要熊布偶作為禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今年做的這個 應該是做得最好的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道從那開始就一直在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.43,0:20:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 其他東西我都不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有點小機關哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有那些 都是大家給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}安潔莉卡 賽門 還有林德爾的都送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}禮物原本都是要當天拆開的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以這些明天再拆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:20:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 先吃晚餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說教就等到晚餐後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他還記著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是你告訴我 我會跟著去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還能買不少東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為有些話只能和同為女孩子的人說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聖誕節似乎本來就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難以置信 我竟然會期待明天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有個可憐的孩子啊
Comment: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.01,0:22:33.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}月は見ていた　欠けてる僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:37.68,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互いを呼び合いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:47.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠回りで　遠い道を歩いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:57.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}引きよせ合う　赤と黒が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:04.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}追いかけ合う　闇と光が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:10.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}二つの対なるもので
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:12.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創られてるよ
